des:
The user account binding operation of L-Home APP could be completed quickly according to the following steps:
1. Download L-Home APP through Apple store or Google play or scan the QR code, then register and login;
2. Open the L-Home APP, click "+" in the upper right corner and select adding devices (smart remote control, RGB led strip, etc.). According to the installation guide, finish the distribution network of the device;
3.Enter the operation interface of smart remote control, and add sub-devices (air conditioner, fan, TV configuration with infrared remote control comes in) according to the interface tips;
4. Log in Amazon Alexa APP, binding the user account of L-Home, then the configured home devices(such as lighting, air conditioning, TV, fan, etc.) would be voice controlled by Echo;

Supported devices
Air conditioning, fan, TV, set-top box, curtain, led strip kits, switch, ceiling light, down light.
